<cb:div>
<pb n="0098a" xml:id="I01.0040.0098a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0098a00" type="honorific"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><cb:docNumber>No. 40</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0098a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>凝禪寺三級浮圖碑</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0098a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0098a0101">凝禪
<lb ed="I" n="0098a02" type="honorific"/>寺三
<lb ed="I" n="0098a03" type="honorific"/>級浮
<lb ed="I" n="0098a04" type="honorific"/><note n="0098001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">啚＝圖【史】</note><note n="0098001" resp="ihp" type="mod">啚【佛拓】，圖【史】</note><app n="0098001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">啚</rdg></app><note n="0098002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">㞢＝之【史】</note><note n="0098002" resp="ihp" type="mod">㞢【佛拓】，之【史】</note><app n="0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0098a05" type="honorific"/>碑頌</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0098b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0098b0101">□纖景凝麗。則海鏡圖<note n="0098003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">朙＝明【史】</note><note n="0098003" resp="ihp" type="mod">朙【佛拓】，明【史】</note><app n="0098003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">明</lem><rdg wit="【原】">朙</rdg></app>。皇秀潛暎。則□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">獎</unclear>□。□□□聖。□薇□而顯淵蹤。現元吉而<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">輝</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0098b02" type="honorific"/>沖旨。故高蹈七步。耀天人<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>儀。駕遊四門。悲生老為苦。啓眉光<note n="0098004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30642"/>＝明【史】</note><note n="0098004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30642"/>【佛拓】，明【史】</note><app n="0098004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">明</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30642"/></rdg></app>於長夜。流齣彩<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">敻</unclear>於重<note n="0098005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">昬＝昏【史】</note><note n="0098005" resp="ihp" type="mod">昬【佛拓】，昏【史】</note><app n="0098005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">昏</lem><rdg wit="【原】">昬</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0098b03" type="honorific"/>玄鑒洞於<note n="0098006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30643"/>＝冥【史】</note><note n="0098006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30643"/>【佛拓】，冥【史】</note><app n="0098006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">冥</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30643"/></rdg></app>機。靈照渙於寂像。<note n="0098b0301" resp="CBETA" type="add">无【CB】，旡【原】【史】</note><app n="0098b0301"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>言<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>論。拂石記年。沙童<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>說。彈指為證。<note n="0098007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30488"/>＝權【史】</note><note n="0098007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30488"/>【佛拓】，權【史】</note><app n="0098007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">權</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30488"/></rdg></app>影哀於群宗。應
<lb ed="I" n="0098b04" type="honorific"/>響悽於類族。靡身不即。即也而流仁。無音不曉。曉也而知覺。斯實不思議<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>至妙也。然<note n="0098008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30644"/>＝化【史】</note><note n="0098008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30644"/>【佛拓】，化【史】</note><app n="0098008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">化</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30644"/></rdg></app>歷
<lb ed="I" n="0098b05" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">世</unclear>二境。教盡四域<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>鄉。靈軒迻軔。遷隱雙樹。<note n="0098009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30645"/>＝金【史】</note><note n="0098009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30645"/>【佛拓】，金【史】</note><app n="0098009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30645"/></rdg></app>顏雖遙。經圖流範。是用育王<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>塔。東<note n="0098010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30646"/>＝土【史】</note><note n="0098010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30646"/>【佛拓】，土【史】</note><app n="0098010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">土</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30646"/></rdg></app>隆基。
<lb ed="I" n="0098b06" type="honorific"/>優闐<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>像。西域彌構。法輪滿世。妙露斯光。但群品異途。行乖殊致。令迷井<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app><note n="0098011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𤢌＝禽【史】</note><note n="0098011" resp="ihp" type="mod">𤢌【佛拓】，禽【史】</note><app n="0098011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">禽</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𤢌</rdg></app>。自亡於木羂。
<lb ed="I" n="0098b07" type="honorific"/>百首<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>鱗。懸鰓於釣庸。貪愛溺於死河。春<note n="0098012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">䗝＝蠶【史】</note><note n="0098012" resp="ihp" type="mod">䗝【佛拓】，蠶【史】</note><app n="0098012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蠶</lem><rdg wit="【原】">䗝</rdg></app>圓絲入繭。自非抽穎神峰。<note n="0098013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30648"/>＝迢【史】</note><note n="0098013" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30648"/>【佛拓】，迢【史】</note><app n="0098013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">迢</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30648"/></rdg></app>然孤秀者。焉能於
<lb ed="I" n="0098b08" type="honorific"/>滄<note n="0098014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𤀰＝滈【史】</note><note n="0098014" resp="ihp" type="mod">𤀰【佛拓】，滈【史】</note><app n="0098014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">滈</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𤀰</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>津而拯彼岸哉。今正信佛弟子趙居士。名融。字祖和。元氏人也。其先與秦同姓。至周
<lb ed="I" n="0098b09" type="honorific"/>穆王造父。有騄駬<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>勳。賜姓趙氏。又匡弼晉□。暨於武靈王。布錦千城。散綺万<note n="0098015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">囻＝國【史】</note><note n="0098015" resp="ihp" type="mod">囻【佛拓】，國【史】</note><app n="0098015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">國</lem><rdg wit="【原】">囻</rdg></app>。郁郁顯於
<lb ed="I" n="0098b10" type="honorific"/>篆冊。穆穆聰至於斯矣。遠祖蘭。漢司徒公征<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">東</unclear>將軍都督內外諸軍事冀州刺史趙郡公。纂
<lb ed="I" n="0098b11" type="honorific"/>珪芳於遐葉。遂因封此焉。居士融。蘊沖惔<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>妙性。如荔□<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>瑤馨。懷珠照寂。若霄漢<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>朗月。
<lb ed="I" n="0098b12" type="honorific"/>雅志貞素。行潔儒流。清風峻遠。栖心<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">文</unclear>史。恒以<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">甘</unclear>禪育命。<note n="0098016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">湌＝餐【史】</note><note n="0098016" resp="ihp" type="mod">湌【佛拓】，餐【史】</note><app n="0098016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">餐</lem><rdg wit="【原】">湌</rdg></app>經養年。<app type="star" corresp="#0098008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">化</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30644"/></rdg></app>無徹迹。入不曷言。霜
<lb ed="I" n="0098b13" type="honorific"/>齡長碧。雪月<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">含</unclear>清。不<note n="0098017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨶳＝窺【史】</note><note n="0098017" resp="ihp" type="mod">𨶳【佛拓】，窺【史】</note><app n="0098017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">窺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨶳</rdg></app>玉帛<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>門。不踐縉紳<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>戶。靖夜閑吟。任運衰榮。卓絕<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">人</unclear>倫。可謂沖摻
<lb ed="I" n="0098b14" type="honorific"/>自然矣。居士融每常嘆曰。<note n="0098018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30651"/>＝蟝【史】</note><note n="0098018" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30651"/>【佛拓】，蟝【史】</note><app n="0098018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蟝</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30651"/></rdg></app>螻無夕命。椿柯<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">亦</unclear>彫零。神飄生滅境。如雀飛空瓶。鄉□覆詠斯
<lb ed="I" n="0098b15" type="honorific"/>文。則淚沾變石。居士融正以妙味自怡。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">何</unclear>假珠瓔<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>榮乎。<note n="0098019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𦃠＝緇【史】</note><note n="0098019" resp="ihp" type="mod">𦃠【佛拓】，緇【史】</note><app n="0098019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">緇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𦃠</rdg></app>侶尚其仁。素伴貴其清。方<note n="0098020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">鼂＝晁【史】</note><note n="0098020" resp="ihp" type="mod">鼂【佛拓】，晁【史】</note><app n="0098020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">晁</lem><rdg wit="【原】">鼂</rdg></app><note n="0098021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𣣽＝欽【史】</note><note n="0098021" resp="ihp" type="mod">𣣽【佛拓】，欽【史】</note><app n="0098021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">欽</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣣽</rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0098b16" type="honorific"/>木蘭<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>泆露兮。夕<app type="star" corresp="#0098016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">餐</lem><rdg wit="【原】">湌</rdg></app>秋菊<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>渃英。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">撟</unclear><note n="0098022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30653"/>＝菌【史】</note><note n="0098022" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30653"/>【佛拓】，菌【史】</note><app n="0098022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">菌</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30653"/></rdg></app>桂以<note n="0098023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">綛＝紉【史】</note><note n="0098023" resp="ihp" type="mod">綛【佛拓】，紉【史】</note><app n="0098023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">紉</lem><rdg wit="【原】">綛</rdg></app>蕙兮。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">索</unclear>胡繩<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>纚纚。安貧樂道。井丹<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>流乎。
<lb ed="I" n="0098b17" type="honorific"/>忠清淳信。子良<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>徒乎。輕<app type="star" corresp="#0098009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30645"/></rdg></app>樹福。須達<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>倫乎。<note n="0098024" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30655"/>＝嗒【史】</note><note n="0098024" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30655"/>【佛拓】，嗒【史】</note><app n="0098024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">嗒</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30655"/></rdg></app>然孤舉<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app><note n="0098025" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB03909"/>＝翰【史】</note><note n="0098025" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB03909"/>【佛拓】，翰【史】</note><app n="0098025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">翰</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB03909"/></rdg></app>。逍遙出塵<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>志。是故鄉彥呼
<lb ed="I" n="0098b18" type="honorific"/><app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>曰居士。融乃怵然而<note n="0098026" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𠺪＝愾【史】</note><note n="0098026" resp="ihp" type="mod">𠺪【佛拓】，愾【史】</note><app n="0098026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">愾</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠺪</rdg></app>曰。觀世<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>歸死也。何異飛蛾<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>夕火焉。慘隼羽<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">度</unclear>牖。悼蝴蝶<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0098b19" type="honorific"/>變靈。怨蟬啼<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>漏促。悲霜蔕而淚盈。即共長兄浮陽太守文<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">奴</unclear>。元氏令文□。邯鄲令貳奴。元
<lb ed="I" n="0098b20" type="honorific"/>氏令靈和。<note n="0098027" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30657"/>＝房【史】</note><note n="0098027" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30657"/>【佛拓】，房【史】</note><app n="0098027"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">房</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30657"/></rdg></app>子令靈宣。長兼參軍<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">市</unclear>□兄弟等。孝友恭良。頤居茂於紫荊。皆宦敘衣冠。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">榮</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">錦</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0098b21" type="honorific"/>百里。率鄉賢道俗二千餘人等。並信敬玄深。體空虛寂。詳造三級浮圖。凝禪寺□構蕭廓。寶
<lb ed="I" n="0098b22" type="honorific"/>堂密靖。層甍耀於霞漢。玉繢<g ref="#CB30758"/>於<note n="0098028" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB07018"/>＝瓊【史】</note><note n="0098028" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB07018"/>【佛拓】，瓊【史】</note><app n="0098028"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">瓊</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB07018"/></rdg></app>珉。飾以丹碧。<note n="0098029" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30658"/>＝雕【史】</note><note n="0098029" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30658"/>【佛拓】，雕【史】</note><app n="0098029"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">雕</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30658"/></rdg></app>以仙形。松柳翠鬱。井級淒涼。鴻翻則雲
<lb ed="I" n="0098b23" type="honorific"/>波。風嘯百籟吟。居士融復衢設義<app type="star" corresp="#0098016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">餐</lem><rdg wit="【原】">湌</rdg></app>。珍<note n="0098030" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">饍＝膳【史】</note><note n="0098030" resp="ihp" type="mod">饍【佛拓】，膳【史】</note><app n="0098030"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">膳</lem><rdg wit="【原】">饍</rdg></app>盈案。<note n="0098031" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30659"/>＝笑【史】</note><note n="0098031" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30659"/>【佛拓】，笑【史】</note><app n="0098031"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">笑</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30659"/></rdg></app>迎愧送。穆於文<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">質</unclear>矣。其處<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">南</unclear>瞻堎埠。霰靃
<lb ed="I" n="0098b24" type="honorific"/><app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>所藂薈。北城峻峙。百王<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>固綿基。東有村□。蓊蔚連煙。西嵢<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">盤</unclear>岌。虜光翳而迴薄。其寺妙
<lb ed="I" n="0098b25" type="honorific"/>像精異。遊<note n="0098032" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">眂＝視【史】</note><note n="0098032" resp="ihp" type="mod">眂【佛拓】，視【史】</note><app n="0098032"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">視</lem><rdg wit="【原】">眂</rdg></app>忘歸。所造<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>福。仰資　皇<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">猷</unclear>□隆。丞相休永。王公百司。師僧父母。識性<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>類。梵
<lb ed="I" n="0098b26" type="honorific"/>水洗心。常生淨樂。居士<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>善。上昇人天。下□鬼壤。鄉義僉言曰。<note n="0098033" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">㫺＝昔【史】</note><note n="0098033" resp="ihp" type="mod">㫺【佛拓】，昔【史】</note><app n="0098033"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">昔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㫺</rdg></app>纖容<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>功。尚詠於<app type="star" corresp="#0098009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30645"/></rdg></app>篇。片
<lb ed="I" n="0098b27" type="honorific"/>瓦<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>施。猶頌於遺陵。況居士融建斯景福。豈<note n="0098034" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30662"/>＝得【史】</note><note n="0098034" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30662"/>【佛拓】，得【史】</note><app n="0098034"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">得</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30662"/></rdg></app>蔑聞哉。恐靈迹勝<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">因</unclear>。空傳無記。故鄉人中兵
<lb ed="I" n="0098b28" type="honorific"/>參軍鄭鑒邑義二千等。慕海春<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>餘韻。羨雙雁<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>追仁。乃相與託鍾山以詮妙軌。刊玄石以
<lb ed="I" n="0098b29" type="honorific"/>颿鴻芳。當使淥竹<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>彩。長搖於紫風。清松<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>碧。永輝於素月。其詞曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0098b30" type="honorific"/><note n="0098035" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𡙎＝皎【史】</note><note n="0098035" resp="ihp" type="mod">𡙎【佛拓】，皎【史】</note><app n="0098035"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">皎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡙎</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0098035"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">皎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡙎</rdg></app>沖覺。寂寂虛清。塵中獨鏡。霧里孤<app type="star" corresp="#0098003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">明</lem><rdg wit="【原】">朙</rdg></app>。龍□現跡。素木歸靈。玄夢垂影。雪山流<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">經</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">殊</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">顏</unclear>同
<lb ed="I" n="0098b31" type="honorific"/>習。分言共聲。<app type="star" corresp="#0098003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">明</lem><rdg wit="【原】">朙</rdg></app>珠泣醉。羊鹿悲嬰。林蘤水淥。<note n="0098036" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">虬＝虯【史】</note><note n="0098036" resp="ihp" type="mod">虬【佛拓】，虯【史】</note><app n="0098036"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">虬</rdg></app>翔雲枝。耆鷲風遠。給孤<app type="star" corresp="#0098008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">化</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30644"/></rdg></app>移。<app type="star" corresp="#0098009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30645"/></rdg></app>粟爰集。文殊
<lb ed="I" n="0098b32" type="honorific"/>來儀。釤梯重秀。枯蓮更猗。遺芳<app type="star" corresp="#0098002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㞢</rdg></app>軌。妙猷仍玄。濁浪澄曦。晌<note n="0098037" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">㬡＝昤【史】</note><note n="0098037" resp="ihp" type="mod">㬡【佛拓】，昤【史】</note><app n="0098037"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">昤</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㬡</rdg></app>凝淵。居士祖和。兄弟貞賢。體
<lb ed="I" n="0098b33" type="honorific"/>茲四空。五有非珍。獎率鄉儒。營斯福田。津流遐劫。果鍾人天。祇菀還日。提河再年。惠風蠲拂。
